producer - consumer binding

producer = src name = Mopeka:ble or mqtt:sub3 or espnow or...

consumer = dest name = alias name for lv_subject string format

string format = json

consumer example - esp/c++
    envtemp = lv_subject + set of UI elements
        tales "temp" and "ts" attributes -> display temperature, hygro

    websocket:
    logger
    teleplot

